      "text": "# Team Ownership\n\n## Mahdi\nProduct decisions, prompt/schema, MVP scope, validation, tradeoffs.\n\n## Designer\nToday page, Reconcile flow, non-judgmental UX, AI Knowledge visual meter.\n\n## Backend\nEvent log, task CRUD, skippable reconcile, daily rollup, weekly review, source tagging, confidence thresholds."
