      "width": 420,
      "height": 460,
      "text": "# Open Questions\n\n- Are validation thresholds realistic for 10–20 testers?\n- How should skip-rate be interpreted?\n- Is the AI Knowledge silhouette/fill visual useful or risky?\n- Confirm MVP scheduling model: goal-linked + planned-for-day only?\n- What confidence model should replace/validate Progressive Bayesian Confidence?\n- What were the exact social evidence posts?"
